    },
    {
      "trigger": "gate_jasmine",
      "description": "Jasmine is not present in the gym until EVENT_JASMINE_RETURNED_TO_GYM is set. This requires the player to obtain SecretPotion in Cianwood City and deliver it to Amphy at the top of Glitter Lighthouse. Only then does Jasmine return and the gym battle becomes available."
