  "notes": "Olivine City is a coastal port town in western Johto. It connects north to Route 39 (Moo Moo Farm direction) and west to Route 40 (ocean route to Cianwood). The Glitter Lighthouse dominates the southeast. The S.S. Aqua departs from Olivine Port post-game to Vermilion City in Kanto. The gym (Steel type, Jasmine) cannot be challenged until after the SecretPotion sidequest at Glitter Lighthouse and Cianwood. Map constants: OLIVINECITY_SAILOR1=0, OLIVINECITY_STANDING_YOUNGSTER=1, OLIVINECITY_SAILOR2=2, OLIVINECITY_OLIVINE_RIVAL=3."
